column5: Hey Pete, how could I possibly forget your birthday. I hope you're having a really good one. Fish mightily and be well my friend. It's also Marc Thorpe's birthday today but I saw him recently and he was in fine shape.
I guess this means if I am going to get my bucket list done I better hurry up since to fish with both of them is on it. Happy Birthday to the two legends.   Art
Happy Birthday Pete  Hope Esther cooked you up something good
I'm in Art .. make it happen   Happy birthday fellas !
Wow !!! You have the same birthday as Skipper D !!! Amazing Happy Birthday Pete !!!
Happy B day dude  A big TKs to Roy for a wonderful supper
Hey, Happy BDay Pete!!! All the best to ya in 2012!!
Now that's a great Birthday present a day and Meal with Roy and Jay.   Art

Hi All,  And Happy New Year to you!  Thanks so much Roy ... Marc was in fine shape? ... and you cooked for him? I sure wish I wasn't 1000+ miles away from you guys.  Happy birthday to you Thorpie ... glad to hear you are in such good shape too!  Pete
Hope you had a great day, Pete. You know the door is always open.
Thankyou Roy!  Your hospitality is awesome and nice to know welcome!  Pete
